data.description: Take a look at this Stonebridge home that features vaulted ceilings and lots of living space in the tiled great room. There is a formal dining room with hardwood floors, as well as beautiful granite counter tops in the spacious kitchen. This beautiful home also features 3-car tandem garage with pull-through, covered patio for shade next to the pool.  There is also a leased solar system to provide relief from those high electric bills!  Hurry and make your appointment to see this beautiful home today!!!
